      "line_id": "intro-1",
      "filename": "intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/fractions/yunxi/intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.67,
      "size": 26640,
      "text": "小朋友们好！欢迎来到分数可视化实验。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "fractions",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-2",
      "filename": "intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/fractions/yunxi/intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.65,
      "size": 42480,
      "text": "你有没有分过蛋糕？把一个蛋糕切成几块，每人拿一块，这就是分数的来源！"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "fractions",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-3",
      "filename": "intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/fractions/yunxi/intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.57,
      "size": 25200,
      "text": "今天，我们要用漂亮的图形来学习分数。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "fractions",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-4",
      "filename": "intro-intro-4.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/fractions/yunxi/intro-intro-4.mp3",
      "duration": 1.34,
      "size": 21456,
      "text": "准备好了吗？让我们开始吧！"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "fractions",
      "section_id": "concept",
      "line_id": "concept-1",
      "filename": "concept-concept-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/fractions/yunxi/concept-concept-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.06,
      "size": 32976,
      "text": "分数由两部分组成：上面的数叫分子，下面的数叫分母。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "fractions",
      "section_id": "concept",
      "line_id": "concept-2",
      "filename": "concept-concept-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/fractions/yunxi/concept-concept-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.49,
      "size": 39888,
      "text": "分母告诉我们把整体分成了多少份。比如分母是4，就是分成4份。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "fractions",
      "section_id": "concept",
      "line_id": "concept-3",
      "filename": "concept-concept-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/fractions/yunxi/concept-concept-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.26,
      "size": 36144,
      "text": "分子告诉我们取了其中的几份。比如分子是1，就是取了1份。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "fractions",
      "section_id": "concept",
      "line_id": "concept-4",
      "filename": "concept-concept-4.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/fractions/yunxi/concept-concept-4.mp3",
      "duration": 1.87,
      "size": 29952,
      "text": "所以四分之一，就是把整体分成4份，取其中的1份。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "fractions",
      "section_id": "concept",
      "line_id": "concept-5",
      "filename": "concept-concept-5.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/fractions/yunxi/concept-concept-5.mp3",
      "duration": 2.31,
      "size": 37008,
      "text": "看饼图！蓝色部分就是我们取的那一份，灰色部分是剩下的。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "fractions",
      "section_id": "visualization",
      "line_id": "vis-1",
      "filename": "visualization-vis-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/fractions/yunxi/visualization-vis-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.18,
      "size": 18864,
      "text": "分数可以用不同的图形来表示。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "fractions",
      "section_id": "visualization",
      "line_id": "vis-2",
      "filename": "visualization-vis-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/fractions/yunxi/visualization-vis-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.47,
      "size": 23472,
      "text": "饼图就像切蛋糕，把圆形分成几块。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "fractions",
      "section_id": "visualization",
      "line_id": "vis-3",
      "filename": "visualization-vis-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/fractions/yunxi/visualization-vis-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.63,
      "size": 26064,
      "text": "条形图就像巧克力棒，把长条分成几段。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "fractions",
      "section_id": "visualization",
      "line_id": "vis-4",
      "filename": "visualization-vis-4.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/fractions/yunxi/visualization-vis-4.mp3",
      "duration": 1.63,
      "size": 26064,
      "text": "网格图就像格子纸，把方块分成几个小格。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "fractions",
      "section_id": "visualization",
      "line_id": "vis-5",
      "filename": "visualization-vis-5.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/fractions/yunxi/visualization-vis-5.mp3",
      "duration": 1.66,
      "size": 26496,
      "text": "不管用哪种图形，表示的分数都是一样的！"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "fractions",
      "section_id": "compare",
      "line_id": "compare-1",
      "filename": "compare-compare-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/fractions/yunxi/compare-compare-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.4,
      "size": 22464,
      "text": "现在来学习怎么比较两个分数的大小。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "fractions",
      "section_id": "compare",
      "line_id": "compare-2",
      "filename": "compare-compare-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/fractions/yunxi/compare-compare-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.18,
      "size": 34848,
      "text": "看图最直观！哪个分数涂色的部分更多，哪个就更大。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "fractions",
      "section_id": "compare",
      "line_id": "compare-3",
      "filename": "compare-compare-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/fractions/yunxi/compare-compare-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.48,
      "size": 39600,
      "text": "比如四分之一和三分之二，三分之二涂色更多，所以三分之二更大。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "fractions",
      "section_id": "compare",
      "line_id": "compare-4",
      "filename": "compare-compare-4.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/fractions/yunxi/compare-compare-4.mp3",
      "duration": 2.8,
      "size": 44784,
      "text": "也可以把分数变成小数来比较。四分之一等于0.25，三分之二约等于0.67。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "fractions",
      "section_id": "compare",
      "line_id": "compare-5",
      "filename": "compare-compare-5.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/fractions/yunxi/compare-compare-5.mp3",
      "duration": 2.09,
      "size": 33408,
      "text": "0.67大于0.25，所以三分之二大于四分之一。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "fractions",
      "section_id": "addition",
      "line_id": "add-1",
      "filename": "addition-add-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/fractions/yunxi/addition-add-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.87,
      "size": 29952,
      "text": "分数加法有一个小技巧：先通分，再相加。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "fractions",
      "section_id": "addition",
      "line_id": "add-2",
      "filename": "addition-add-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/fractions/yunxi/addition-add-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.49,
      "size": 23904,
      "text": "通分就是把两个分数变成相同的分母。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "fractions",
      "section_id": "addition",
      "line_id": "add-3",
      "filename": "addition-add-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/fractions/yunxi/addition-add-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.08,
      "size": 33264,
      "text": "比如四分之一加三分之二，公共分母是4乘3等于12。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "fractions",
      "section_id": "addition",
      "line_id": "add-4",
      "filename": "addition-add-4.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/fractions/yunxi/addition-add-4.mp3",
      "duration": 1.99,
      "size": 31824,
      "text": "四分之一变成十二分之三，三分之二变成十二分之八。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "fractions",
      "section_id": "addition",
      "line_id": "add-5",
      "filename": "addition-add-5.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/fractions/yunxi/addition-add-5.mp3",
      "duration": 2.21,
      "size": 35424,
      "text": "分子相加：3加8等于11。结果是十二分之十一！"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "fractions",
      "section_id": "multiplication",
      "line_id": "mul-1",
      "filename": "multiplication-mul-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/fractions/yunxi/multiplication-mul-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.21,
      "size": 35280,
      "text": "分数乘法比加法简单！分子乘分子，分母乘分母。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "fractions",
      "section_id": "multiplication",
      "line_id": "mul-2",
      "filename": "multiplication-mul-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/fractions/yunxi/multiplication-mul-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.18,
      "size": 18864,
      "text": "比如四分之一乘三分之二。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "fractions",
      "section_id": "multiplication",
      "line_id": "mul-3",
      "filename": "multiplication-mul-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/fractions/yunxi/multiplication-mul-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.18,
      "size": 34848,
      "text": "分子：1乘2等于2。分母：4乘3等于12。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "fractions",
      "section_id": "multiplication",
      "line_id": "mul-4",
      "filename": "multiplication-mul-4.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/fractions/yunxi/multiplication-mul-4.mp3",
      "duration": 1.49,
      "size": 23760,
      "text": "结果是十二分之二，约分后是六分之一。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "fractions",
      "section_id": "multiplication",
      "line_id": "mul-5",
      "filename": "multiplication-mul-5.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/fractions/yunxi/multiplication-mul-5.mp3",
      "duration": 1.42,
      "size": 22752,
      "text": "分数乘法的意思是\"取一部分的一部分\"。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "fractions",
      "section_id": "simplify",
      "line_id": "simp-1",
      "filename": "simplify-simp-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/fractions/yunxi/simplify-simp-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.68,
      "size": 26928,
      "text": "约分就是把分数变得更简单，但大小不变。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "fractions",
      "section_id": "simplify",
      "line_id": "simp-2",
      "filename": "simplify-simp-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/fractions/yunxi/simplify-simp-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.26,
      "size": 36144,
      "text": "方法是：找到分子和分母的最大公约数，然后同时除以它。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "fractions",
      "section_id": "simplify",
      "line_id": "simp-3",
      "filename": "simplify-simp-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/fractions/yunxi/simplify-simp-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.78,
      "size": 28512,
      "text": "比如十二分之四，4和12的最大公约数是4。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "fractions",
      "section_id": "simplify",
      "line_id": "simp-4",
      "filename": "simplify-simp-4.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/fractions/yunxi/simplify-simp-4.mp3",
      "duration": 1.7,
      "size": 27216,
      "text": "分子4除以4等于1，分母12除以4等于3。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "fractions",
      "section_id": "simplify",
      "line_id": "simp-5",
      "filename": "simplify-simp-5.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/fractions/yunxi/simplify-simp-5.mp3",
      "duration": 2.71,
      "size": 43344,
      "text": "所以十二分之四约分后是三分之一。看图，它们涂色的面积是一样的！"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "fractions",
      "section_id": "parameters",
      "line_id": "param-1",
      "filename": "parameters-param-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/fractions/yunxi/parameters-param-1.mp3",
      "duration": 0.86,
      "size": 13824,
      "text": "现在轮到你来试试了！"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "fractions",
      "section_id": "parameters",
      "line_id": "param-2",
      "filename": "parameters-param-2.mp3",
