      "duration": 2.92,
      "size": 46656,
      "text": "在右边的控制面板，你可以选择不同的操作：比较、加法、乘法或约分。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "fractions",
      "section_id": "parameters",
      "line_id": "param-3",
      "filename": "parameters-param-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/fractions/yunxi/parameters-param-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.07,
      "size": 33120,
      "text": "拖动滑块可以改变分子和分母。看看图形会怎么变化？"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "fractions",
      "section_id": "parameters",
      "line_id": "param-4",
      "filename": "parameters-param-4.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/fractions/yunxi/parameters-param-4.mp3",
      "duration": 2.65,
      "size": 42480,
      "text": "试试切换不同的图形：饼图、条形图、网格图，哪个最容易理解？"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "fractions",
      "section_id": "parameters",
      "line_id": "param-5",
      "filename": "parameters-param-5.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/fractions/yunxi/parameters-param-5.mp3",
      "duration": 1.5,
      "size": 24048,
      "text": "多试几组数字，你会发现分数的规律！"
    },
    {
